            <p>The fault reported in this issue occurs only if the domxml extension is enabled.</p>

<p>The domxml extension is for PHP 4, and it contains known conflicts with the PHP 5 DOM extension.  The domxml extension is not supported, developed, or maintained anymore.</p>

<p>Based on what I have read in the following links, the PHP 5 DOM extension is better, faster, and it is a supported extension in PHP 5.</p>

